chunks.html_content:
Undergraduates and postgraduates can get help with the costs of their teacher training.

You can get student finance for the following full or part-time teacher training courses:

  • initial teacher training (ITT) - including early years
  • school-centred initial teacher training (SCITT)
chunks.plain_content:
Teacher training funding
Undergraduates
Undergraduates and postgraduates can get help with the costs of their teacher training.
You can get student finance for the following full or part-time teacher training courses:

  initial teacher training (ITT) - including early years
  school-centred initial teacher training (SCITT)

chunks.html_content:
You may be able to get student finance for the following full or part-time teacher training courses:

  • ITT - not including early years
  • Postgraduate Certificate of Education (PGCE)
  • SCITT

You’ll need to apply for undergraduate student finance to get funding for your teacher training.
chunks.plain_content:
Teacher training funding
Postgraduates
You may be able to get student finance for the following full or part-time teacher training courses:

  
ITT - not including early years
  Postgraduate Certificate of Education (PGCE)
  SCITT

You’ll need to apply for undergraduate student finance to get funding for your teacher training.

chunks.html_content: If you already have qualified teacher status, you cannot get an undergraduate tuition fee loan.
chunks.plain_content:
Teacher training funding
Postgraduates
If you already have qualified teacher status, you cannot get an undergraduate tuition fee loan.

chunks.html_content: You cannot apply for student finance if you’re a postgraduate early years ITT trainee. Your fees will be paid by DfE. You may also be eligible for an early years ITT bursary.
chunks.plain_content:
Teacher training funding
Postgraduates
Early years ITT

You cannot apply for student finance if you’re a postgraduate early years ITT trainee. Your fees will be paid by DfE. You may also be eligible for an early years ITT bursary.

chunks.html_content: You may also be able to get a postgraduate training bursary or an undergraduate training bursary from the Department for Education (DfE).
chunks.plain_content:
Teacher training funding
Bursaries
You may also be able to get a postgraduate training bursary or an undergraduate training bursary from the Department for Education (DfE).
